function fff(lam, x0)
return -1/(1-szift(lam,x0))
end

function derfpox0(lam,x0)

function test(x0)
return fff(lam, x0)
end
return ForwardDiff.derivative(test, x0)
end


function derxpox0(lam, x0)
G=1
ρ0=rho0
Δ=delta
λ=lam 
γ=gamma
if x0<=xb


ret= ((G ^ -1 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1) ^ (-1//3) * cbrt(G ^ -1 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1 * (1 + -2 * λ * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2) * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2) + 6 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2 * λ ^ 2)))

elseif x0>xb

ret=((G ^ -1 * x0 ^ 3 * xb ^ -3 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1) ^ (2//3) * (-3 * x0 ^ 3 + 8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) ^ -1 * (6 * pi * λ ^ 2 + -2 * λ * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * (G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) ^ (-1//2) * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) + G ^ -1 * x0 ^ 3 * xb ^ -3 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1) ^ (-2//3) * (x0 ^ 3 * (-3 + 3 * λ * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2)) + 8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2))

end
return ret
end

function derPRAWOpolam(lam, x0)

end  

function derxpox0polam2(lam, x0)

end

end


function derxpox0polam(lam,x0)
xb=10
G=1
ρ0=rho0
Δ=delta
λ=lam 
γ=gamma    

if x0<=xb    
ret=(2//3 * (G ^ -1 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1) ^ (2//3) * (G ^ -1 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1 * (1 + -2 * λ * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2) * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2) + 6 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2 * λ ^ 2)) ^ (-2//3) * (-1 * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2) * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2) + 6 * pi * G * Δ * λ * ρ0 * γ ^ 2))

    
    
elseif x0>xb
ret=(-1//3 * x0 ^ -3 * (G ^ -1 * x0 ^ 3 * xb ^ -3 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1) ^ (5//3) * (3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) ^ (-1//2) * (6 * pi * λ ^ 2 + -2 * λ * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * (G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) ^ (-1//2) * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) + G ^ -1 * x0 ^ 3 * xb ^ -3 * Δ ^ -1 * γ ^ -2 * ρ0 ^ -1) ^ (-5//3) * (-3 * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * x0 ^ 3 * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) + 2 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2 * (6 * λ * sqrt(3 + -8 * pi * G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) + 16 * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2) + -9 * sqrt(2) * sqrt(pi) * λ ^ 2 * sqrt(G * Δ * ρ0 * x0 ^ -3 * xb ^ 3 * γ ^ 2))))
    end

return ret
end

using DifferentialEquations
xpoczU=10


function rozwiazanie(s1,lamstar)

if s1<0    
    
function calyproblem(du, u, p, s)
du[1] = -derxpox0(u[1], u[2])
du[2] = -gamma*sqrt(delta)
du[3] = u[3]*derxpox0polam(u[1], u[2])
end


        
        
u0 = [lamstar; xpoczU; -1]

sspan=(0,-s1 ) ## 0 20

prob3 = ODEProblem(calyproblem, u0, sspan, abstol = 1e-6, reltol = 1e-6)
sol3 = solve(prob3)

return sol3(-s1)
        
    elseif s1>=0        
        
function calyproblem2(du, u, p, s)
du[1] = derxpox0(u[1], u[2])
du[2] = gamma*sqrt(delta)
du[3] = -u[3]*derxpox0polam(u[1], u[2])
end

u02 = [lamstar; xpoczU; -1]

sspan2=(0,s1+1 )  ### 0 60

prob32 = ODEProblem(calyproblem2, u02, sspan2, abstol = 1e-6, reltol = 1e-6)
sol32 = solve(prob32)

return sol32(s1)        
        
end
end

function bisection(f, a, b, tol)
    
    if sign(f(a)) == sign(f(b))
        error("function has the same sign at given endpoints")
    end

    mid = (a + b)/2

    while abs(f(mid)) > tol

        sign(f(mid)) == sign(f(a)) ? a=mid : b=mid
            
        mid = (a + b)/2

    end

    return mid
    
end

xpoczV=10
function rozwiazanieV(s1,lamstar)

if s1<0    
    
function calyproblem(du, u, p, s)
du[1] = -derxpox0(u[1], u[2])
du[2] = gamma*sqrt(delta)
du[3] = u[3]*derxpox0polam(u[1], u[2])
end

u0 = [lamstar; xpoczV; 1]

sspan=(0,-s1 ) 

prob3 = ODEProblem(calyproblem, u0, sspan, abstol = 1e-6, reltol = 1e-6)
sol3 = solve(prob3)

return sol3(-s1)
        
    elseif s1>=0        
        
function calyproblem2(du, u, p, s)
du[1] = derxpox0(u[1], u[2])
du[2] = -gamma*sqrt(delta)
du[3] = -u[3]*derxpox0polam(u[1], u[2])
end

u02 = [lamstar; xpoczV; 1]

sspan2=(0, s1+1) 

prob32 = ODEProblem(calyproblem2, u02, sspan2, abstol = 1e-6, reltol = 1e-6)
sol32 = solve(prob32)

return sol32(s1)        
        
end
end

end

######### TIMELIKE SINGULARITY V2


function trajx(T)
return x(T/(gamma*sqrt(delta)),10)
end

M= 4/3*pi*xb^3*rho0
ff = x -> 1 - 2*G*M/x + 4*G^2*M^2*gamma^2*delta/x^4


xs1=find_zeros(ff,(0,100) )[1]
xs2=find_zeros(ff,(0,100) )[2]


inte =x-> 1/(ff(x) )


xszift = x-> sqrt(2*G*M*(x^3-2*G*M*gamma^2*delta)/x^4)

function calkX(x)

if x<xs1
ret = quadgk( x1->inte(x1),  1e-15, x)[1]

elseif xs1<x<xs2
ret = quadgk( x1->inte(x1),  0, xs1-1e-7)[1] + quadgk( x1->inte(x1),  xs1+1e-7, x)[1]

elseif xs2<x

ret = quadgk( x1->inte(x1), 0, xs1-1e-7)[1] + quadgk( x1->inte(x1), xs1+1e-12, xs2-1e-7)[1] + quadgk( x1->inte(x1), xs2+1e-7, x)[1] 
end
    
return ret
end

calkX(5)


intet = T-> 1/ff(trajx(T))

tsin1 = find_zeros(intet, (-100,100) )[1]
tsin2 = find_zeros(intet, (-100,100) )[2]
tsin3 = find_zeros(intet, (-100,100) )[3]
tsin4 = find_zeros(intet, (-100,100) )[4]



function calkt(T)

if T<tsin1
ret= quadgk( T1->intet(T1), 0, tsin1+1e-7 )[1] + quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin1-1e-7, T )[1]




elseif tsin1<T<tsin2
ret =  quadgk( T1->intet(T1), 0, T )[1]

elseif tsin2<T<tsin3
ret= quadgk( T1->intet(T1), 0, tsin2-1e-7 )[1] + quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin2+1e-7, T)[1]

elseif tsin3<T<tsin4
ret = (quadgk( T1->intet(T1), 0, tsin2-1e-7 )[1] + quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin2+1e-7, tsin3-1e-7 )[1]
            +quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin3+1e-7, T )[1] )

elseif tsin4<T
ret = (quadgk( T1->intet(T1), 0, tsin2-1e-7 )[1] + quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin2+1e-7, tsin3-1e-7 )[1]+
            quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin3+1e-7, tsin4-1e-7 )[1]
    +quadgk( T1->intet(T1), tsin4+1e-7, T)[1] )
end

return ret
end

upow = T -> calkt(T) - calkX(trajx(T))
vpow = T -> calkt(T) + calkX(trajx(T))



tabT=range(tsin1+1e-7, tsin2-1e-7, length=500)


tabu = upow.(tabT)

tabT = vcat(tsin1+1e-15,tabT,tsin2-1e-15)
tabu = vcat( 3000 ,tabu, -3000 )


tabT=reverse(tabT)
tabu=reverse(tabu)

ToduSIN=linear_interpolation(tabu, tabT)


tabTv=range(tsin3+1e-7, tsin4-1e-7, length=500)
tabv= vpow.(tabTv)


tabTv=vcat(tsin3+1e-15,tabTv, tsin4-1e-15 )
tabv=vcat(3000, tabv, -3000)


tabTv=reverse(tabTv)
tabv=reverse(tabv)

TodvSIN=linear_interpolation(tabv,tabTv)

function auTRAJ(T)
